Slice is a 2-year effort to build the protocolÂ for decentralized commerce. At the time of writing we:
- Created the Slice protocol and deployed 55 related contracts on Base;
- Built the Slice web interface and API at slice.so, used to interact with the protocol;
- Developed the Slice subgraph as the public API for tracking products and purchases;
- Attracted a growing user base, emphasizing our impact and value within the Optimism ecosystem;
- Worked alongside Coinbase to improve the UX of onchain commerce and onboard traditional merchants to Base and the Optimism ecosystem.
